00:08.050 --> 00:10.380
(Shin Eun Soo, Park Ye Young, Kwak Min Gyu, Bang Jae Min)

00:34.840 --> 00:39.909
(Summer Strike)

00:45.520 --> 00:47.449
(Summer Strike, Episode 2)

00:47.450 --> 00:49.189
(Lee Yeo Reum)

01:08.939 --> 01:11.010
(Hair Salon)

01:11.209 --> 01:12.938
(Welcome)

01:12.939 --> 01:14.680
(Restaurant)

02:08.900 --> 02:12.438
- Hey, I have ice cream at home! - I have some at home too!

02:12.439 --> 02:13.739
I'll see you later.

02:13.740 --> 02:15.409
- Okay. - Sure.

02:15.639 --> 02:17.938
(Angok Public Library)

02:17.939 --> 02:20.509
(Angok Public Library)

02:25.150 --> 02:28.719
- Hey, let's race there. - What? Race there?

03:03.759 --> 03:06.689
(Checkouts and Returns)

03:17.569 --> 03:21.610
(Literature)

03:39.219 --> 03:40.930
("The Old Man and the Sea")

03:49.469 --> 03:51.939
"But man is not made for defeat."

03:53.840 --> 03:56.069
"A man can be destroyed..."

03:56.409 --> 03:57.840
"but not defeated."

04:03.650 --> 04:06.219
Yes. I should live here.

04:17.300 --> 04:18.399
Hey.

04:28.370 --> 04:29.439
Excuse me, miss.

04:33.910 --> 04:36.180
Is there a real estate agency around here?

04:44.589 --> 04:46.860
Oh, I'm sorry.

04:48.759 --> 04:49.959
Sorry.

04:58.199 --> 05:01.338
(Angok Public Library)

05:01.339 --> 05:03.268
Hey, pass it to me.

05:03.269 --> 05:05.980
- Hey! - Pass the ball to me.

05:07.949 --> 05:09.378
- Hey. - Hey.

05:09.379 --> 05:10.419
Old lady with the bag.

05:10.420 --> 05:11.518
- Can you kick it to us? - Kick the ball!

05:11.519 --> 05:13.419
- Over here! Kick it to us. - Here!

05:13.420 --> 05:15.849
- Me? - Yes. You're the only one here!

05:15.850 --> 05:18.289
- Kick the ball to us. - Kick the ball to us.

05:18.290 --> 05:20.489
- Kick it already. Hurry. - Hey.

05:20.490 --> 05:22.389
- I'm not that old! - Over here!

05:32.839 --> 05:34.240
- Hey, Dae Bum! - Dae Bum!

05:34.740 --> 05:37.309
- Hey. Stay with me. - Dae Bum!

05:37.310 --> 05:39.278
- Stay with me. Are you okay? - Are you all right?

05:39.279 --> 05:41.579
- That must hurt! - Are you all right?

05:41.850 --> 05:44.049
- I'm sorry. - Oh, no. It's red.

05:44.050 --> 05:46.379
- Oh, no. Hey. - Hey. Do you want to die?

05:46.819 --> 05:49.489
- Hey. Do you have a death wish? - What's that?

05:49.490 --> 05:51.588
- How dare you hurt him? - How dare you?

05:51.589 --> 05:53.060
- I'm sorry. - What was that?

05:53.420 --> 05:55.860
- Leave! Get lost! - I'm sorry.

06:03.129 --> 06:04.600
(Discount Store, Bridge)

06:05.170 --> 06:06.339
It's a map.

06:15.610 --> 06:17.379
I said I was good.

06:17.850 --> 06:20.689
If you see those thugs again, drop my name.

06:20.850 --> 06:21.888
Bae Sung Min, the bronze medallist...

06:21.889 --> 06:22.889
at the National Junior Sports Festival.

06:22.890 --> 06:24.159
- I'm leaving now. - Wait.

06:24.160 --> 06:25.758
- Hey. - Put your head in here.

06:25.759 --> 06:27.828
- Hey. - I got it.

06:27.829 --> 06:31.360
- Hey. Hold on a second. - Gosh.

06:32.000 --> 06:34.729
- Oh, my back. Hold on. - Hey. Your back.

06:34.730 --> 06:36.669
- Like this. - Okay. Gosh.

06:36.670 --> 06:37.699
Hello.

06:40.139 --> 06:42.569
Do you sell super glue here?

06:43.209 --> 06:45.110
Check the section with the brushes.

06:46.439 --> 06:47.509
Are you all right?

06:47.980 --> 06:49.550
You should have been more careful.

06:50.050 --> 06:51.420
Gosh. This is bad.

06:52.079 --> 06:54.889
It's been a while since I did that. My back hurts.

06:56.949 --> 07:00.360
I must have overdone myself. My goodness.

07:17.579 --> 07:19.379
- Hey. - What?

07:21.509 --> 07:22.680
The glue is two dollars.

07:23.180 --> 07:24.519
It's not that.

07:24.920 --> 07:26.920
What? Where are you going, Bom?

07:27.519 --> 07:29.050
I'm leaving because your products are awful.

07:29.889 --> 07:31.119
That brat.

07:31.120 --> 07:32.790
If she didn't want to buy anything, she shouldn't have come inside.

07:33.019 --> 07:34.889
I told you. It's two dollars.

07:35.129 --> 07:36.430
Okay.

07:38.160 --> 07:40.329
- Are you all right? - Here.

07:40.569 --> 07:41.629
Thanks.

07:42.269 --> 07:43.300
Bye.

07:44.899 --> 07:46.500
- Bye. - Bye.

07:48.269 --> 07:49.310
Wait.

07:51.009 --> 07:53.410
I got you. Come here.

08:06.689 --> 08:08.629
You brats! Go play somewhere else!

08:08.959 --> 08:11.529
You'd better not hit my car with the ball. Or else!

08:11.860 --> 08:12.958
Beat it!

08:12.959 --> 08:14.429
Let's go!

08:14.430 --> 08:15.470
Gosh.

08:21.170 --> 08:22.569
No one is in the library, right?

08:36.190 --> 08:38.590
How much longer do they want me to rot in Angok?

08:39.220 --> 08:42.289
Why won't they transfer me out of here?

08:43.190 --> 08:44.860
Dae Bum, I didn't make it again.

08:45.330 --> 08:47.100
I can't transfer to the county office again.

08:49.169 --> 08:50.399
This is so annoying.

08:50.669 --> 08:52.769
Why won't they transfer me?

08:55.509 --> 08:57.740
I want to go to Seoul.

08:58.539 --> 09:00.379
I hate it here!

09:08.590 --> 09:11.690
Whatever. Gosh. I'm so sick of this.

09:12.919 --> 09:14.759
I only bought the glue.

09:15.490 --> 09:18.600
Well, we'll have to check to see if you're telling the truth.

09:19.129 --> 09:20.199
What's this?

09:20.200 --> 09:22.529
Why are you carrying a blanket?

09:23.570 --> 09:25.639
Are you on a backpacking trip or something?

09:25.970 --> 09:26.970
What's this?

09:31.309 --> 09:32.309
And this?

09:33.580 --> 09:34.950
- Sung Min. - Yes.

09:35.409 --> 09:37.110
Check her pockets.

09:39.279 --> 09:42.419
- Right. Let me check your pockets. - Gosh.

09:43.250 --> 09:45.059
- Let me check... - What are you doing?

09:45.889 --> 09:47.159
Let's check your pockets.

09:50.429 --> 09:51.799
There's nothing.

09:55.700 --> 09:56.899
This is odd.

09:57.570 --> 09:59.669
I paid good money for that thing.

10:01.909 --> 10:02.970
Hey.

10:04.080 --> 10:05.210
What's this?

10:08.409 --> 10:10.350
Come on. Are you kidding me?

10:10.750 --> 10:12.648
Why did you put that on your backpack?

10:12.649 --> 10:14.889
I didn't put it there.

10:16.289 --> 10:17.389
A 4B pencil?

10:18.720 --> 10:20.019
Did she have a 4B pencil?

10:21.860 --> 10:24.330
Why are you treating her like a thief? Goodness.

10:25.860 --> 10:29.069
(Discount Store)

10:29.070 --> 10:31.740
(Discount Store, Bridge)

10:31.870 --> 10:34.839
Young people these days have such creative minds.

10:34.840 --> 10:38.009
So they have no problem fixing houses to suit their needs.

10:39.139 --> 10:41.778
The landlady... Be careful there.

10:41.779 --> 10:43.509
Is electricity installed here?

10:43.710 --> 10:45.820
Well... Gosh. What was that?

10:49.919 --> 10:51.559
How much is the monthly rent here?

10:51.820 --> 10:55.059
It's 500 dollars. But I can try to lower it for you.

10:55.360 --> 10:56.629
The deposit is 20,000 dollars.

11:00.659 --> 11:03.970
The deposit is 2,000 dollars. And the rent is 200 dollars.

11:04.539 --> 11:06.500
I can lower it to 170 dollars.

11:07.139 --> 11:08.209
I see.

11:08.210 --> 11:10.369
But you said it was a shared bathroom, right?

11:10.370 --> 11:12.480
Yes. It's down here. We can go together...

11:14.110 --> 11:17.049
Goodness. What is he scratching? Why is he smelling that?

11:19.220 --> 11:22.850
I'm sorry. But I can't let you move in here.

11:23.090 --> 11:25.620
(Angok Realtor)

11:31.000 --> 11:32.059
That's a shame.

11:38.139 --> 11:39.269
Wait.

11:40.139 --> 11:42.840
This was my wife's idea.

11:43.110 --> 11:45.039
I have one more place to show you.

11:45.580 --> 11:46.639
Where?

11:46.909 --> 11:49.950
It's difficult to explain it. Why don't we go and see it?

11:51.649 --> 11:52.649
This way.

11:56.320 --> 11:57.590
It's this building.

11:59.389 --> 12:00.689
It's not a house.

12:00.690 --> 12:02.690
What? No.

12:04.659 --> 12:05.929
It's not even locked.

12:08.769 --> 12:10.100
Come inside.

12:11.570 --> 12:13.039
All right. This way.

12:20.210 --> 12:21.480
Come on in.

12:23.210 --> 12:24.418
This used to be...

12:24.419 --> 12:27.950
the biggest billiard hall in our neighbourhood.

12:28.120 --> 12:31.258
Gosh. It's nice and spacious. You can even play soccer here.

12:31.259 --> 12:32.419
Kick it.

12:33.960 --> 12:37.758
When they built this building, they used a lot of cement.

12:37.759 --> 12:39.628
So it's a sturdy building.

12:39.629 --> 12:41.029
So it won't collapse.

12:42.929 --> 12:46.538
Right. You should check out the rooftop on a sunny day.

12:46.539 --> 12:48.469
It's really bright up there.

12:48.470 --> 12:50.809
You can dry your laundry in no time.

12:53.679 --> 12:54.909
That's not all.

12:56.779 --> 13:00.649
You can occupy the entire building.

13:02.690 --> 13:04.220
This entire building?

13:05.159 --> 13:06.259
Yes.

13:07.629 --> 13:10.429
Then no one lives in this building?

13:11.529 --> 13:13.960
Well, I guess you can say that.

13:15.870 --> 13:18.139
Maybe, it's not a good idea for a young lady to stay here alone.

13:23.470 --> 13:26.210
How much is the rent?

13:26.909 --> 13:29.308
The rent? Do you like it?

13:29.309 --> 13:31.749
Gosh. My wife was right.

13:31.750 --> 13:33.980
I knew you would be different.

13:34.049 --> 13:36.690
All right. You know what? I'll go right now...

13:36.850 --> 13:39.119
and lock down the rental price with the owner.

13:39.120 --> 13:41.460
Wait here. Okay?

13:42.389 --> 13:43.389
But...

13:49.929 --> 13:52.439
Hey, I'm here.

13:52.440 --> 13:53.970
Hey. You're here.

13:55.570 --> 13:58.409
I needed to talk to you about something.

13:59.279 --> 14:01.679
Gosh. You didn't have to bring me anything.

14:02.779 --> 14:03.850
Gosh.

14:05.049 --> 14:06.919
- What's this about? - Listen.

14:07.820 --> 14:10.989
I was showing houses to a young lady...

14:10.990 --> 14:12.559
from Seoul today.

14:12.860 --> 14:15.889
And I suddenly thought about you.

14:17.029 --> 14:18.200
Why?

14:22.570 --> 14:24.570
Why don't we show her your building?

14:25.100 --> 14:26.240
What do you mean?

14:26.740 --> 14:28.569
I don't feel good about the first floor.

14:28.570 --> 14:29.768
But the billiard hall on the second floor.

14:29.769 --> 14:32.740
Gosh. Chang Soo is going to buy it. It's already a done deal.

14:33.309 --> 14:35.950
Besides, people can't live there.

14:37.350 --> 14:41.190
Well, does she seem like a nice lady?

14:41.389 --> 14:43.450
Yes. She seemed really honest.

14:44.590 --> 14:48.389
But still. If she finds out what happened...

16:08.539 --> 16:11.308
Yangyang became popular because young people moved there.

16:11.309 --> 16:13.778
Think about the rent and property value there.

16:13.779 --> 16:15.808
You know how much they went up.

16:15.809 --> 16:19.418
You brat. Where have you been instead of working at the store?

16:19.419 --> 16:22.149
Well, I dropped by Chang Soo's for a second.

16:22.419 --> 16:23.850
What brings you here?

16:24.590 --> 16:27.490
Well, I needed to talk to your father.

16:28.960 --> 16:33.200
Sung Min, we can't sell the building to Chang Soo.

16:34.059 --> 16:37.429
Come on. What? Dad.

16:37.629 --> 16:39.240
Have you gone senile?

16:40.070 --> 16:42.610
I was with Chang Soo just now. I talked him into buying it.

16:43.240 --> 16:46.339
He even prepared the down payment to sign the contract this week.

16:46.340 --> 16:47.908
Oh, right. I forgot about the contract.

16:47.909 --> 16:49.579
It's not like I signed any contracts yet.

16:49.580 --> 16:52.048
I changed my mind. What's he going to do about it?

16:52.049 --> 16:54.619
He has a point. You need a contract for it to be legally binding.

16:54.620 --> 16:56.119
Come on, Mr. Kwak!

16:56.120 --> 16:58.690
You know what? After listening to him,

16:58.919 --> 17:01.529
I realized it would be a huge loss if I sold it for that price.

17:02.559 --> 17:06.499
Dad, it's been years since anyone rented that building.

17:06.500 --> 17:10.129
You know what? You should go and check it out with Mr. Kwak.

17:10.130 --> 17:11.368
Go where?

17:11.369 --> 17:13.470
Go and sign the contract at the billiard hall.

17:14.299 --> 17:15.469
I heard a nice fridge came in today.

17:15.470 --> 17:17.979
So I need to go downtown to pick up the refrigerator.

17:17.980 --> 17:19.479
- Gosh. - Okay. Drive safely.

17:19.480 --> 17:21.910
- Bye. - Dad, what contract?

17:28.690 --> 17:30.989
- Who is it? - You startled me.

17:30.990 --> 17:32.419
Who is it?

17:32.420 --> 17:35.358
- Mr. Kwak? - Honey. What's wrong?

17:35.359 --> 17:36.630
- Over there. - What?

17:38.200 --> 17:40.959
Who are you? What are you doing here?

17:40.960 --> 17:44.229
I came here to look at the building. Who are you?

17:44.230 --> 17:46.669
- What? - You came to look at this building?

17:46.670 --> 17:48.568
Chang Soo!

17:48.569 --> 17:50.140
- Come on. - Chang Soo!

17:51.140 --> 17:52.440
Hey, Sung Min.

17:52.710 --> 17:55.348
You told me we could come here and measure the place.

17:55.349 --> 17:57.649
But you've been showing this building? Seriously.

17:57.650 --> 18:01.149
No. That's not true. I just found out too.

18:01.150 --> 18:02.848
Let's talk about this outside.

18:02.849 --> 18:04.588
Talk about what? We can do it here.

18:04.589 --> 18:06.288
Well, I have a client here.

18:06.289 --> 18:07.389
- A client? - What?

18:07.390 --> 18:09.258
You have nothing to worry about.

18:09.259 --> 18:10.689
- Let's go outside. - Hey.

18:10.690 --> 18:13.328
- Come on. Please? - Hey! Are you serious?

18:13.329 --> 18:16.298
- Let go of me. - No. I just found out too.

18:16.299 --> 18:19.169
- Hey! Are you serious right now? - Come on.

18:19.170 --> 18:20.299
Are you all right?

18:21.410 --> 18:22.640
You must have been quite startled.

18:23.569 --> 18:26.339
Since all the lights are out, let's go to the window.

18:27.140 --> 18:29.279
Gosh. Why is she screaming like that?

18:29.450 --> 18:32.179
- Come here. - Hey, stop pushing me!

18:32.180 --> 18:33.679
You need to watch your steps!

18:33.680 --> 18:35.450
I can walk just fine. Don't push me.

18:35.849 --> 18:39.358
Hey, who's that woman? What do you mean, "client?"

18:39.359 --> 18:42.288
What? Is your dad going to sell it to her to make...

18:42.289 --> 18:43.660
a bit more money off this?

18:44.289 --> 18:47.298
Listen. She came here to rent this place.

18:47.299 --> 18:49.669
Do you think she'll rent this? Don't worry about it.

18:49.670 --> 18:53.670
But why did you show this building without our permission?

18:53.769 --> 18:56.139
Hey, do you think that makes any sense?

18:56.140 --> 18:57.508
Hey, I didn't bring her here.

18:57.509 --> 18:59.339
And I'm not planning to look for a tenant either.

18:59.579 --> 19:02.180
It was all my father's and Mr. Kwak's idea.

19:02.509 --> 19:04.979
- I told you. - What's he talking about?

19:04.980 --> 19:07.420
- Gosh. - I won't let my father do this.

19:07.650 --> 19:10.318
Chang Soo, take her back to your store.

19:10.319 --> 19:13.159
I'll take care of this and head over there.

19:13.160 --> 19:16.129
Gosh, Sung Min. Don't mess this up. Okay?

19:16.130 --> 19:18.528
Of course. Don't you know who I am? I'm good at what I do.

19:18.529 --> 19:20.199
- Okay. - You're cracking me up.

19:20.200 --> 19:22.329
Let's go. You should go back inside too.

19:22.769 --> 19:25.098
- That little... - Come on!

19:25.099 --> 19:27.039
- You can't break that! - Okay.

19:28.069 --> 19:31.538
Did I do something wrong?

19:31.539 --> 19:33.910
Gosh, no. Not at all.

19:33.940 --> 19:36.409
There was a misunderstanding.

19:36.410 --> 19:39.180
You don't have to worry about them. Don't mind them.

19:39.250 --> 19:41.789
Mr. Kwak!

19:42.890 --> 19:44.758
Mr. Kwak. What did you tell my dad?

19:44.759 --> 19:46.758
How did you get him to change his mind?

19:46.759 --> 19:49.989
Well, come on. Don't be so rude. We have a client here.

19:49.990 --> 19:52.730
This is the son of the building owner.

19:52.859 --> 19:55.269
- You... - Discount Store?

19:55.700 --> 19:58.639
Look. I used to be an athlete.

19:58.640 --> 20:00.470
So I hate beating around the bush.

20:01.609 --> 20:04.778
All right. So do you even know where you're moving into?

20:04.779 --> 20:06.380
- Be quiet. Hey. - Do you?

20:06.579 --> 20:08.679
It's been 20 years since this place has been vacant.

20:08.680 --> 20:09.880
Why do you think so?

20:10.450 --> 20:11.619
Twenty years?

20:11.819 --> 20:14.149
Stop it. Are you seriously doing this right now?

20:14.150 --> 20:16.950
I already talked to your father. He's on board with this.

20:17.089 --> 20:19.818
- You said she was the tenant. - What's this about?

20:19.819 --> 20:21.259
It's nothing.

20:21.660 --> 20:23.029
Nothing, my foot.

20:24.059 --> 20:26.858
- Someone died in here. - What?

20:26.859 --> 20:29.499
Can you live in a building where someone died? I can't!

20:29.500 --> 20:30.970
Are you seriously doing this?

20:31.500 --> 20:35.139
Well, this is your decision to make.

20:35.140 --> 20:37.440
But nothing happened after that.

20:37.670 --> 20:38.740
Mr. Kwak.

20:39.710 --> 20:43.348
Just look at her face. She's terrified.

20:43.349 --> 20:45.848
You know what? Let's not do this in this dark building.

20:45.849 --> 20:47.848
Let's talk about it outside. Okay? There might be ghosts in here.

20:47.849 --> 20:49.318
- Come on. - Okay?

20:49.319 --> 20:51.919
If you keep this up, I'll talk to your father about this!

20:51.920 --> 20:53.719
Go ahead. Do it.

20:53.720 --> 20:56.389
You know what? I'll be honest. I can't believe this.

20:56.390 --> 20:58.258
Why did you bring her here?

20:58.259 --> 20:59.598
There are other perfectly liveable houses.

20:59.599 --> 21:01.569
- Are you trying to scam her? - Miss.

21:01.970 --> 21:03.200
Fifty dollars.

21:03.769 --> 21:04.839
- What? - What?

21:05.339 --> 21:07.769
The monthly rent here is 50 dollars.

21:07.900 --> 21:10.308
- What did you say? - Fifty dollars?

21:10.309 --> 21:13.338
I wouldn't have brought you here unless this place had an upside.

21:13.339 --> 21:15.750
Mr. Kwak. Are you serious?

21:15.880 --> 21:18.679
I got the owner of this building...

21:18.680 --> 21:21.149
to rent this place to you for 50 dollars.

21:21.150 --> 21:23.190
And in exchange for your work to maintain this place.

21:23.420 --> 21:25.858
My father agreed to 50 dollars for the monthly rent?

21:25.859 --> 21:26.890
Yes!

21:27.559 --> 21:29.129
- Yes! - Okay. I'll call him.

21:29.130 --> 21:30.489
You. Be smart about this.

21:30.490 --> 21:31.599
Fifty dollars.

21:32.160 --> 21:33.829
To stay here for a year,

21:34.900 --> 21:36.569
it would cost 600 dollars.

21:37.430 --> 21:39.670
So what's it going to be?

21:42.069 --> 21:44.569
Then I'll take this place.

21:44.880 --> 21:45.979
What?

21:45.980 --> 21:48.078
- Yes. Excellent! - Dad.

21:48.079 --> 21:50.749
- Hello? Dad. - You know what? Let me pray...

21:50.750 --> 21:52.219
- I'm at the building. - for your good fortune.

21:52.220 --> 21:53.719
- The rent is 50 dollars? - Father.

21:53.720 --> 21:56.919
- She will settle down here. - What?

21:56.920 --> 21:59.588
- Bless with your love and glory. - Come on, Dad!

21:59.589 --> 22:01.389
- Dad! - Amen.

22:01.390 --> 22:02.960
Come on. This is nuts!

22:03.289 --> 22:05.299
Let's go, Sung Min.

22:06.230 --> 22:08.130
Hold on a second.

22:08.230 --> 22:10.598
- Did you even try using the toilet? - Go away.

22:10.599 --> 22:12.399
Even if you take a dump here, it won't flush.

22:12.400 --> 22:13.599
You can't take a shower here.

22:14.170 --> 22:16.308
How are you going to live in a place like this?

22:16.309 --> 22:18.308
You really should reconsider!

22:18.309 --> 22:21.750
(Bae Young Ho, Lee Yeo Reum)

22:22.849 --> 22:24.720
I'm glad you like the place.

22:24.950 --> 22:27.149
- Thanks. - Ma'am.

22:27.150 --> 22:29.989
All right. You can wire the annual rent, 600 dollars now.

22:29.990 --> 22:31.049
Okay.

22:34.829 --> 22:37.259
- I just wired it to you. - Check it.

22:41.130 --> 22:42.400
What about your commission?

22:42.500 --> 22:44.529
Gosh, don't mention it. It's all right.

22:45.869 --> 22:47.569
Just live a good life there.

22:47.740 --> 22:49.269
- Thank you. - Here.

22:52.180 --> 22:56.809
By the way, can I move in tonight?

22:57.309 --> 22:58.480
Tonight?

22:59.480 --> 23:01.649
But there's no electricity. Nothing works in the building.

23:01.650 --> 23:02.650
It's okay.

23:03.890 --> 23:06.119
Well, your lease does start today.

23:06.619 --> 23:08.589
You're ridiculous. Gosh.

23:09.690 --> 23:11.730
- Come on. - Sung Min.

23:12.960 --> 23:14.230
Give her the key.

23:19.670 --> 23:21.440
Here you go. Okay?

23:21.769 --> 23:24.608
Honey, remember what I asked? Bring that now.

23:24.609 --> 23:25.940
Okay.

23:27.480 --> 23:29.278
The lights don't work in the building.

23:29.279 --> 23:30.979
Gosh, thank you.

23:30.980 --> 23:32.980
- Live a good life there. - Okay.

23:33.779 --> 23:36.118
- That punk. Okay. - Bye.

23:36.119 --> 23:38.259
- Bye. - Bye.

23:43.190 --> 23:44.259
Well,

23:45.400 --> 23:49.329
thank you for telling me what happened in the building.

23:51.430 --> 23:53.900
If I had found out later, it would have been scarier.

23:56.569 --> 23:57.710
Whatever.

23:58.009 --> 24:01.480
If things break down there, you can fix it yourself.

24:02.009 --> 24:05.519
If you can't live there anymore, don't hesitate to leave. Okay?

24:06.950 --> 24:07.980
Okay.

24:21.460 --> 24:22.829
I have a home now.

25:16.920 --> 25:19.720
After quitting my job in that split second,

25:20.690 --> 25:23.589
I just stayed in bed for two days.

25:25.500 --> 25:26.700
I was scared.

25:28.130 --> 25:32.200
I couldn't think of what to do. Nothing came to my mind.

25:38.539 --> 25:41.180
I decided to leave Seoul first.

25:42.380 --> 25:45.680
Staying in a place like this without a job would be too much.

26:00.529 --> 26:02.669
I didn't have the heart to throw out Jae Dong's things before.

26:02.670 --> 26:04.829
But I finally got rid of them.

26:09.539 --> 26:12.579
And as for my stuff,

26:12.880 --> 26:15.480
I decided to only keep things that would fit into one backpack.

26:18.250 --> 26:20.518
While going through my stuff,

26:20.519 --> 26:22.089
I realized I had bought so many things.

26:22.589 --> 26:25.259
The tea mugs I collected just because they looked cute.

26:26.059 --> 26:28.759
The plates I've only used once for my housewarming party.

26:33.359 --> 26:35.769
The clothes I had bought but didn't even know I had.

26:36.869 --> 26:39.970
The cheap shoes I habitually bought at the shops by the bus terminal.

26:41.940 --> 26:45.809
From each category, I only picked one item I absolutely needed.

26:46.710 --> 26:48.139
It was even more competitive...

26:48.140 --> 26:49.950
than the interviews to join those top companies.

26:51.509 --> 26:54.990
I listed the things I didn't need online, and they sold right away.

27:01.119 --> 27:02.190
Goodbye,

27:03.029 --> 27:04.660
my 20mÂ² life.

27:13.599 --> 27:15.440
Before this trip is over,

27:16.710 --> 27:18.140
I want to find the answer.

27:20.509 --> 27:21.750
On how...

27:22.309 --> 27:24.109
I should live my life from now on.

27:34.789 --> 27:36.490
(Alarm, 5am)

27:39.900 --> 27:42.368
(Alarm, 1 Selected, 5am)

27:42.369 --> 27:43.930
(No Alarms)

27:59.180 --> 28:00.779
This is the perfect spot to stare at the sky.

28:17.569 --> 28:18.839
Hello.

28:21.670 --> 28:22.910
Hello.

28:25.339 --> 28:26.509
How may I help you?

28:26.910 --> 28:30.410
What can I do to get a membership card for this library?

28:31.950 --> 28:34.649
To do that, you need an address in this area.

28:34.650 --> 28:35.950
Yes, I have one.

28:36.150 --> 28:38.319
- Oh, did you recently move here? - Yes.

28:38.859 --> 28:40.059
He'll help you.

28:40.789 --> 28:41.789
Okay.

28:41.790 --> 28:43.259
(Checkouts and Returns)

28:51.700 --> 28:52.799
Well...

28:54.299 --> 28:56.539
Were you all right yesterday?

29:01.240 --> 29:02.279
I'm sorry.

29:04.349 --> 29:07.519
Oh, and thank you for the map.

29:12.660 --> 29:15.490
What's she talking about? Map? Med?

29:26.869 --> 29:27.970
Here.

29:30.140 --> 29:31.980
Oh. Isn't this the billiard hall?

29:34.009 --> 29:35.579
You live here?

29:36.750 --> 29:37.750
Yes.

29:44.150 --> 29:45.390
Thank you.

29:48.190 --> 29:50.160
(Library Membership Card, Lee Yeo Reum)

29:53.160 --> 29:54.659
(Checkouts and Returns)

29:54.660 --> 29:56.670
What? How is she living there?

30:01.500 --> 30:02.569
Hi.

30:37.339 --> 30:39.740
- Excuse me. - Your bag is over there.

30:40.440 --> 30:41.779
It's not about that.

30:45.779 --> 30:49.490
Hey, this is my spot. Don't sit here from now on.

30:50.319 --> 30:52.920
Kim Bom, be quiet.

30:53.319 --> 30:55.329
Why does she only tell me to be quiet?

31:06.900 --> 31:07.970
Wait.

31:23.819 --> 31:24.890
Hello?

31:25.490 --> 31:28.559
Can you come out for a moment?

31:29.130 --> 31:30.328
Who is this?

31:30.329 --> 31:31.759
Come downstairs, and you'll see.

31:32.359 --> 31:33.829
Who are you to tell me to come out...

31:35.269 --> 31:36.269
Hello?

31:37.369 --> 31:40.839
Kim Bom, are you messing with me? Talk outside.

31:41.200 --> 31:42.609
Gosh, she's so annoying.

31:46.940 --> 31:51.180
(Angok Public Library)

31:58.890 --> 31:59.959
What's up?

31:59.960 --> 32:02.829
I think our phones got switched.

32:03.329 --> 32:04.329
What?

32:05.529 --> 32:06.559
Here.

32:09.230 --> 32:10.299
What?

32:10.529 --> 32:12.869
Both phones are caseless, so we probably got confused.

32:16.240 --> 32:17.309
Your grandmother?

32:18.440 --> 32:19.509
Me?

32:19.980 --> 32:21.680
Can't you tell? I'm in high school.

32:23.250 --> 32:25.279
No. I'm talking about the wallpaper on your phone.

32:28.319 --> 32:30.150
Who told you that you could snoop through my phone?

32:31.390 --> 32:33.420
- I'm sorry. - You'd better watch out.

32:35.289 --> 32:36.329
Excuse me.

32:38.960 --> 32:39.960
What now?

32:43.269 --> 32:44.299
It's nothing.

32:46.369 --> 32:47.839
(Angok Public Library)

32:52.839 --> 32:54.180
I should just go eat something.

32:56.809 --> 32:59.150
- This looks delicious. - Enjoy.

32:59.950 --> 33:02.349
- Hey, where have you been? - Let me pour you one.

33:02.890 --> 33:04.690
- Oh, my. - Hey.

33:04.849 --> 33:06.019
What would you like to order?

33:07.460 --> 33:08.730
Oh, hello.

33:10.329 --> 33:11.359
What do you want?

33:12.930 --> 33:14.799
I'll have one serving of sundaeguk.

33:14.930 --> 33:16.529
One sundaeguk!

33:16.769 --> 33:18.569
Okay, coming right up!

33:18.869 --> 33:21.069
- This order is ready. - Okay!

33:25.539 --> 33:26.640
Enjoy.

33:39.190 --> 33:41.058
Excuse me. Can we get another bottle of soju?

33:41.059 --> 33:42.358
Sure!

33:42.359 --> 33:45.598
- Just one more drink. - Is it okay to drink this much?

33:45.599 --> 33:47.730
- Just today. - Let's drink.

33:48.029 --> 33:50.328
- Don't drink so much. - All right.

33:50.329 --> 33:51.399
Come on. This is fine.

33:51.400 --> 33:54.338
- We must drink today. - This soju tastes so good.

33:54.339 --> 33:57.309
Yes. Here, I won't worry about what others may think of me.

33:57.539 --> 33:58.608
I'll do whatever I want.

33:58.609 --> 34:00.740
- Isn't the meat so good today? - Excuse me.

34:00.839 --> 34:03.349
- The meat is to die for. - What else would you like?

34:03.549 --> 34:04.650
Ma'am.

34:05.980 --> 34:07.980
I'd like a bottle of soju.

34:08.420 --> 34:10.250
I told you. Don't do that.

34:10.489 --> 34:12.018
Okay, I heard you.

34:12.019 --> 34:13.959
It's not even a big deal.

34:13.960 --> 34:16.788
- But that guy said... - No.

34:16.789 --> 34:18.389
All right, sure.

34:25.070 --> 34:26.070
This is nice.

34:26.940 --> 34:28.539
Hot, cold, hot, cold.

34:28.969 --> 34:30.610
Who came up with this?

34:42.190 --> 34:44.589
Let's just do that for today.

34:44.590 --> 34:47.089
- Why make such a fuss? - Why don't you help him a little?

34:47.090 --> 34:48.859
Well, I was just...

34:48.860 --> 34:50.860
The same goes for you. About that thing...

34:52.090 --> 34:54.229
Oh, that? But if you're too busy...

34:54.230 --> 34:56.569
- They said they'd take care of it. - I see.

34:56.570 --> 34:59.368
No, they said they didn't have time.

34:59.369 --> 35:03.340
- Really? Okay. - You need to get that sorted out.

35:03.469 --> 35:06.280
I know. I'm trying.

35:14.119 --> 35:15.179
The taste of true adulthood.

35:17.590 --> 35:20.389
(Jeil Restaurant)

35:20.690 --> 35:23.230
- Thank you for the food! - That was great!

35:23.289 --> 35:26.460
Thanks for coming. I'll put it on your tab! Bye!

35:28.099 --> 35:29.300
All right.

35:37.769 --> 35:39.440
(Soju)

35:41.179 --> 35:43.579
I can't believe they didn't finish their fish cake.

35:50.590 --> 35:51.789
She's really something.

36:02.199 --> 36:04.769
(Angok Public Library)

36:54.079 --> 36:55.920
Why am I here?

36:59.360 --> 37:01.460
- Bye. - Bye!

37:01.889 --> 37:03.960
- Thank you for the delicious food! - Thank you.

37:04.530 --> 37:08.658
(10 hours ago)

37:08.659 --> 37:11.230
Goodness. That young lady got drunk in broad daylight.

37:13.539 --> 37:16.639
(Restaurant)

37:17.909 --> 37:19.039
Hey, get the ball!

37:21.409 --> 37:23.679
- Hey! - No!

37:26.750 --> 37:28.779
- Dae Bum, let's do it again. - Wait.

37:28.780 --> 37:30.288
- Where are you going? - Dae Bum.

37:30.289 --> 37:33.619
- Hey. - What are you doing?

37:33.760 --> 37:34.960
Hey, wait!

38:05.219 --> 38:08.018
- Hey, look at her. - Hey, look!

38:08.019 --> 38:10.360
- She's so drunk! - Shall I mimic her?

38:11.460 --> 38:13.928
- Hey, look at her face. - Guys, let's play!

38:13.929 --> 38:15.698
- Let's play! - Hey!

38:15.699 --> 38:17.229
- Ready or not, rock-paper-scissors! - Rock-paper-scissors!

38:17.230 --> 38:18.530
Boys, keep it down!

38:19.099 --> 38:20.669
Catch me if you can!

38:20.670 --> 38:22.569
There, I caught you!

38:22.570 --> 38:25.539
- I caught you? - What? What is this?

38:25.840 --> 38:26.979
Is she drunk?

38:26.980 --> 38:29.909
- Oh, look! - Hey, she passed out.

38:31.380 --> 38:33.448
- What is this? - Hey.

38:33.449 --> 38:36.049
- Look at her hair! - It looks like a snake.

38:36.050 --> 38:37.689
Yes!

38:37.690 --> 38:40.090
Excuse me. What are you doing?

38:40.619 --> 38:43.288
- It's Medusa, not a snake. - Right, Medusa!

38:43.289 --> 38:45.488
- Hey, these days... - She must be out of her mind.

38:45.489 --> 38:47.598
Well, maybe she really is out of her mind.

38:47.599 --> 38:49.299
Oh, I'm at the library.

38:49.300 --> 38:50.629
My gosh. What's with her?

38:50.630 --> 38:52.939
- Hey, look. - Why did she come to the library?

38:52.940 --> 38:54.599
Gosh, I should go home.

38:55.710 --> 38:57.940
- Can't you keep your eyes open? - Kids, move aside.

38:58.239 --> 39:00.409
You can't come here drunk.

39:01.710 --> 39:03.750
- I'm sorry. - Okay!

39:05.380 --> 39:07.980
- Let's play! - Stop, kids. Let go.

39:10.889 --> 39:12.689
Hey, not there!

39:12.690 --> 39:14.788
- We'll play here! - No, not there!

39:14.789 --> 39:15.960
Hey, Dae Bum!

39:16.230 --> 39:18.059
I have to go home.

39:19.429 --> 39:21.099
I have to go home...

39:24.599 --> 39:25.900
Gosh, this is crazy.

39:26.369 --> 39:28.769
I need to go home.

39:31.969 --> 39:33.010
What's this?

39:38.250 --> 39:40.150
Gosh, why did I drink?

39:42.889 --> 39:43.889
It's 3am?

39:52.860 --> 39:53.900
Hello?

39:55.869 --> 39:58.599
I'm locked in here! Let me out!

39:58.900 --> 40:00.969
Hello? What should I do?

40:03.739 --> 40:04.769
My phone.

40:14.679 --> 40:15.719
Stay away.

40:16.090 --> 40:18.219
Don't come close. Stop!

40:18.349 --> 40:19.590
Stop!

40:25.190 --> 40:26.230
You're that librarian.

40:34.099 --> 40:35.239
Thank you.

40:50.650 --> 40:54.519
By the way, why are you still here?

40:57.329 --> 40:58.630
Is it because of me?

41:00.530 --> 41:01.599
I'm sorry.

41:09.570 --> 41:11.710
You woke up.

41:12.210 --> 41:14.609
We have to wait until 8am tomorrow...

41:14.610 --> 41:17.579
to use the electricity and open the door.

41:18.650 --> 41:20.780
So make yourself at home and get some rest until then.

41:22.820 --> 41:25.690
Oh, he can't speak.

41:27.860 --> 41:32.030
But why didn't you wake me up?

41:36.429 --> 41:39.670
Dae Bum, I'm off. Tidy up and get going, okay?

41:40.239 --> 41:41.239
Bye!

41:41.240 --> 41:42.539
(7 hours ago)

41:44.340 --> 41:45.769
Thank you. I'm off!

42:56.750 --> 42:59.210
Oh, you probably tried to wake me up but couldn't.

43:01.420 --> 43:02.619
You should get some sleep.

43:24.369 --> 43:26.709
If you want to read some books,

43:26.710 --> 43:29.480
go to the far-right corner by the window.

43:29.750 --> 43:31.250
It's the brightest spot.

43:34.050 --> 43:35.480
Thank you.

43:53.300 --> 43:54.340
This...

44:00.280 --> 44:01.340
Excuse me.

44:03.179 --> 44:04.280
Are you here?

44:10.289 --> 44:12.519
Oh, there you are.

44:14.690 --> 44:15.789
Hey.

44:17.329 --> 44:19.329
You can stop.

44:24.170 --> 44:26.639
I just wanted to return this to you.

44:31.139 --> 44:33.039
That's why I came here, but...

44:37.250 --> 44:41.349
Then I'll just use this and return it to you in the morning.

44:46.219 --> 44:47.519
Good night.

44:51.460 --> 44:52.489
Actually...

44:54.130 --> 44:56.900
Could I use the restroom?

45:07.610 --> 45:10.409
The restroom is outside.

45:12.610 --> 45:16.349
What? If the restroom is outside, why did he give me water to drink?

45:17.949 --> 45:19.789
He gave me the water but didn't even have a sip himself.

45:20.690 --> 45:23.059
No, just shake it off.

45:23.489 --> 45:25.730
I should stop thinking that I need to use the restroom.

45:48.179 --> 45:51.449
(Sorting Room)

46:02.530 --> 46:03.730
It's almost morning.

46:05.030 --> 46:06.340
Almost...

46:08.800 --> 46:09.940
Hang in there.

46:15.510 --> 46:16.750
Just a little longer...

46:20.079 --> 46:21.119
Please...

46:33.260 --> 46:35.530
If I let my guard down at the end, it's game over.

46:36.199 --> 46:37.670
I definitely should not run.

46:38.300 --> 46:40.369
Once it starts coming out, it can't be stopped.

47:32.420 --> 47:33.719
Take care.

47:50.570 --> 47:55.340
(Angok Public Library)

48:18.500 --> 48:21.070
(Angok Public Library)

48:21.269 --> 48:22.699
My gosh.

48:23.610 --> 48:25.469
- What is that? - Wait.

48:27.139 --> 48:28.239
What are they doing?

48:29.179 --> 48:30.179
Your bag.

48:35.449 --> 48:37.349
Oh, right. My bag.

48:40.960 --> 48:44.190
Hold on. He just spoke, didn't he?

48:44.690 --> 48:46.530
What? He can speak?

48:47.460 --> 48:49.799
(Angok Public Library)

48:49.800 --> 48:53.000
Dae Bum, what was that about? Hey!

49:05.809 --> 49:10.320
How much did she drink that she fell asleep at the library?

49:11.320 --> 49:12.749
You're weird too.

49:12.750 --> 49:14.989
You could've just gone home. Why did you stay here all night too?

49:16.159 --> 49:18.059
You can't even talk in front of strangers.

49:20.760 --> 49:21.829
Hey.

49:22.829 --> 49:24.900
Go home and wash up. Take this home too.

49:26.800 --> 49:29.039
My mom made ginseng tea and a bunch of other things for you.

49:30.269 --> 49:32.170
I haven't even finished the things she gave me last time.

49:32.769 --> 49:34.408
She's trying to win you over.

49:34.409 --> 49:36.610
Call her. She's upset because you haven't called her.

49:37.750 --> 49:39.750
Give her my thanks.

49:39.980 --> 49:42.150
- Okay. - Don't forget!

49:42.280 --> 49:43.420
Okay, I will.

49:48.190 --> 49:49.219
Did he hear it?

49:51.090 --> 49:52.159
He must have, right?

49:52.929 --> 49:54.699
Of course, he heard it.

49:55.400 --> 49:56.698
I'm so embarrassed.

49:56.699 --> 49:58.929
Oh, no. What should I do?

49:59.269 --> 50:01.269
This is really embarrassing.

50:13.150 --> 50:14.820
I'm so embarrassed.

50:31.099 --> 50:34.599
Fine. I have nothing more to lose anyway.

50:35.739 --> 50:37.070
No more regrets.

50:37.409 --> 50:39.039
I'll live my life to the fullest.

50:41.239 --> 50:42.710
I can do it!

50:46.050 --> 50:47.179
I can do it.

51:36.329 --> 51:39.269
(Summer Strike)

51:39.429 --> 51:42.169
That woman is renting the billiard hall for 50 dollars a month.

51:42.170 --> 51:43.369
Does that make sense to you?

51:43.440 --> 51:45.038
The water pipe burst.

51:45.039 --> 51:47.639
I clearly told you that you'd have to fix everything on your own.

51:47.980 --> 51:49.738
- She slept at the library... - Oh, no!

51:49.739 --> 51:51.980
and damaged some books too. She's a hot mess.

51:53.449 --> 51:56.078
No one in this neighbourhood is fond of you.

51:56.079 --> 51:57.789
Watch your conduct.

51:57.920 --> 51:59.618
Don't think you can live here for a long time.

51:59.619 --> 52:01.218
Move out. That will be better for everyone's sake.

52:01.219 --> 52:03.460
Why that troublemaker, of all people?

52:03.760 --> 52:05.259
Give her back the rent she paid.

52:05.260 --> 52:06.429
Let's kick her out.
